data.description: Shackleburg Farms Subdivision! Welcome to this inviting one and a half story home, conveniently located for easy access to Anderson, Greenville, and Easley. Boasting a modern design with neutral colors throughout, this residence offers a serene atmosphere for comfortable living.   Key Features:   Open Concept Living: The open living, dining, and kitchen area creates a seamless flow, perfect for entertaining or everyday family life.  Bedrooms: 4 spacious bedrooms provide ample accommodation for families or guests.  Bathrooms: Enjoy the convenience of 2 full bathrooms.  Master Suite: Retreat to the wonderful master suite, complete with a large walk-in closet for all your storage needs.  Bonus Room: Upstairs, discover a versatile bonus room with its own walk-in closet, ideal for use as a playroom, office, or additional living space.  Covered Porch: Relax and unwind on the covered porch, overlooking the level yard and providing a serene outdoor space for enjoying the fresh air.  Convenience: With its convenient location, this home offers easy access to Anderson, Greenville, and Easley, ensuring you're never far from shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Highly sought after Wren Schools!   Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this delightful home yours. Schedule your showing today!
